{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"58022af936","title":"向共产党进一言","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"afb8e3dca7","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":6,"articleId":"58022af936"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"76e509622b","name":"徐福均"},{"id":"b27d1719a6","name":"南京林学院"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a4b667af60","type":"title","text":"向共产党进一言","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58022af936"},{"id":"6f7b79fba9","type":"authors","text":"南京林学院徐福均","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58022af936"},{"id":"33bc5d0c5e","type":"paragraph","text":"徐福均已将他写的“向共产党进一言”的文章交给学生会，从六方面揭露其所谓“一些不平的现实”并提出九项要求。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58022af936"},{"id":"8c04654966","type":"subtitle","text":"“一些不平的现实”","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58022af936"},{"id":"375b565bd9","type":"paragraph","text":"1、一党专政，以党代政；","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58022af936"},{"id":"295021a202","type":"paragraph","text":"2、党员高人一等，视群众为落后分子；","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58022af936"},{"id":"8dead96e94","type":"paragraph","text":"3、在共产党没有克服不了困难标题下，出现了不懂装懂的外行装内行的现象；","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58022af936"},{"id":"f625f91e10","type":"paragraph","text":"4、与民主党派长期共存，有名无实；","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58022af936"},{"id":"e5600fc1a0","type":"paragraph","text":"5、民主气氛不够，自由空气不浓；","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58022af936"},{"id":"f49523f0a0","type":"paragraph","text":"6、责人则严，责己从宽。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58022af936"},{"id":"d0c6631c9e","type":"subtitle","text":"九项要求","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58022af936"},{"id":"5e5f486e09","type":"paragraph","text":"1、大民主自由，今后的选举和统一分配工作应由同学自己作主；","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58022af936"},{"id":"708795cf6d","type":"paragraph","text":"2、要求博爱平等。目前只有对党的尊，没有对群众的敬，应提倡互敬友爱合作；","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58022af936"},{"id":"7baf593287","type":"paragraph","text":"3、对学生的鉴定应全部公开；","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58022af936"},{"id":"9e4c208e52","type":"paragraph","text":"4、立即成立平反委员会，恢复被错斗者的名誉及当众烧毁不符事实的资料，一切不得暗留底稿。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58022af936"},{"id":"2e134a59be","type":"paragraph","text":"5、民主党派应扩大且有职有权；学校亦成立民主党派吸收青年参加，民主党派应和党平级的领导我们，要听听民主人士的政见和治国大纲；","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58022af936"},{"id":"77e3b1b071","type":"paragraph","text":"6、建立由教授为核心的校务委员会来领导全院的教学工作，反对以政治代替业务；","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58022af936"},{"id":"d4a3ce2055","type":"paragraph","text":"7、建立学生代表制，代表应全部由民主方式产生，党群应分开选举；","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58022af936"},{"id":"e3efd32f1d","type":"paragraph","text":"8、紧缩党的机构，取缔各系党支书脱产制，今后党的常规活动费应由党自己负担，不得由国库开支；","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58022af936"},{"id":"d067f5a7a4","type":"paragraph","text":"9、迅速解决建院问题。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58022af936"},{"id":"188b5aee64","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：1957年6月8日新华通讯社编《内部参考》。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58022af936"}],"page":{"id":"7085e45f9b","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58022af936","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}